Weevac 6 bụ ụdị ihe ndina e mepụtara maka ibu ụmụ ọhụrụ, dịka n'ụlọ ọgwụ ma ọ bụ maka ịkwaga ndị ọrịa
Weevac 6 bụ onye a mụrụ na Canada bụ Wendy Murphy mepụtara n'afọ 1985
O nwetara echiche ime ya mgbe ọ na-ekiri ihe gbasara ala ọma jijiji nke Mexico City, na-eche ihe mere na enweghị ngwaọrụ mwepụ maka ụmụ ọhụrụ.
35 na miniseries CBC Ihe mepụtara Canada kacha mma.
